    - single-building penalty (if enabled)
    - strong off-profile type penalty when room type is outside baseline mix
    - penalty when a pick worsens type fit
- Added stronger off-profile guardrail:
  - Large non-baseline room types are strongly discouraged as SF-only fillers.
