  - Search uses weighted candidate utility (type-family alignment, support/storage penalties, single-building preference, SF gap pressure) and iterative trim-to-range.
  - Returns repaired in-range room set when found, reducing strict-fit dead-end failures.
- Kept existing strict repair pass sequence (`baseline`, `repair A`, `repair B`, `repair C`) and layered this as a local option-level salvage step.
